snippet.title: Expedition Zero | Release Date & Demo Announcement
snippet.description:
Expedition Zero — survival horror set in the anomaly zone in the heart of Siberia.
Face the dreadful forest monster and find a way to defeat it. Reveal the secrets of the lost expedition and your mysterious enemy.
It’s either hunt or be hunted.
Launching March 24th.
Play free Demo on Steam Next Fest NOW!
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1247570/Expedition_Zero/
Discord: https://discord.gg/WHRXQ5BH
